{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/technical/medium/2021-08-08_How-to-use-Why-Did-You-Render-library-in-React-Native-a95121978a75/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Yajana Rao"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"eef2a625-e1b0-5823-99ec-1710f7504a6b","excerpt":"why-did-you-render can be used to detect unnecessary re renders in react native.  Setup Install why-did-you-render package for your react native project Using…","html":"<p><em>why-did-you-render</em> can be used to detect unnecessary re renders in react native.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b87c64f127e057ebf601f89b29554fc6/4b190/1__WhR0GNM__wrfEawQ4HfU2ZQ.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.89189189189189%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1  WhR0GNM  wrfEawQ4HfU2ZQ\"\n        title=\"1  WhR0GNM  wrfEawQ4HfU2ZQ\"\n        src=\"/static/b87c64f127e057ebf601f89b29554fc6/1c72d/1__WhR0GNM__wrfEawQ4HfU2ZQ.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b87c64f127e057ebf601f89b29554fc6/a80bd/1__WhR0GNM__wrfEawQ4HfU2ZQ.jpg 148w,\n/static/b87c64f127e057ebf601f89b29554fc6/1c91a/1__WhR0GNM__wrfEawQ4HfU2ZQ.jpg 295w,\n/static/b87c64f127e057ebf601f89b29554fc6/1c72d/1__WhR0GNM__wrfEawQ4HfU2ZQ.jpg 590w,\n/static/b87c64f127e057ebf601f89b29554fc6/4b190/1__WhR0GNM__wrfEawQ4HfU2ZQ.jpg 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Setup</h3>\n<p>Install <a href=\"https://github.com/welldone-software/why-did-you-render\">why-did-you-render</a> package for your react native project</p>\n<p><strong>Using Npm</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install @welldone-software/why-did-you-render --save-dev</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Using Yarn:</strong></p>\n<p>yarn add —dev <a href=\"http://twitter.com/welldone\" title=\"Twitter profile for @welldone\">@welldone</a>-software/why-did-you-render</p>\n<p>Create <code class=\"language-text\">wdyr.js</code> file in root directory of your project</p>\n<p>Setting flag <code class=\"language-text\">trackAllPureComponents</code> will enable logging for all pure components.</p>\n<p>You can track a component by setting <code class=\"language-text\">whyDidYouRender</code> to true</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/736a460f07a424e4bab6dfb6acb8bcca/5a190/1__4evAFZ5JpCQco3iibdkeXQ.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 89.86486486486487%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1  4evAFZ5JpCQco3iibdkeXQ\"\n        title=\"1  4evAFZ5JpCQco3iibdkeXQ\"\n        src=\"/static/736a460f07a424e4bab6dfb6acb8bcca/fcda8/1__4evAFZ5JpCQco3iibdkeXQ.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/736a460f07a424e4bab6dfb6acb8bcca/12f09/1__4evAFZ5JpCQco3iibdkeXQ.png 148w,\n/static/736a460f07a424e4bab6dfb6acb8bcca/e4a3f/1__4evAFZ5JpCQco3iibdkeXQ.png 295w,\n/static/736a460f07a424e4bab6dfb6acb8bcca/fcda8/1__4evAFZ5JpCQco3iibdkeXQ.png 590w,\n/static/736a460f07a424e4bab6dfb6acb8bcca/5a190/1__4evAFZ5JpCQco3iibdkeXQ.png 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Import <code class=\"language-text\">wdyr</code> as the first import in index.js</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4c9474cb4aba28a927dae9b5dae85384/3dd3e/1____LIu6rbQpiJvMbpj8C8RXA.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.432432432432435%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1    LIu6rbQpiJvMbpj8C8RXA\"\n        title=\"1    LIu6rbQpiJvMbpj8C8RXA\"\n        src=\"/static/4c9474cb4aba28a927dae9b5dae85384/fcda8/1____LIu6rbQpiJvMbpj8C8RXA.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4c9474cb4aba28a927dae9b5dae85384/12f09/1____LIu6rbQpiJvMbpj8C8RXA.png 148w,\n/static/4c9474cb4aba28a927dae9b5dae85384/e4a3f/1____LIu6rbQpiJvMbpj8C8RXA.png 295w,\n/static/4c9474cb4aba28a927dae9b5dae85384/fcda8/1____LIu6rbQpiJvMbpj8C8RXA.png 590w,\n/static/4c9474cb4aba28a927dae9b5dae85384/3dd3e/1____LIu6rbQpiJvMbpj8C8RXA.png 595w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Run the application and you should be able to see the logs</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/727db4899b27ba045e53f860e3bfad31/37523/1__nA3n6X__jp8CuSoDywDCLhg.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.08108108108108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1  nA3n6X  jp8CuSoDywDCLhg\"\n        title=\"1  nA3n6X  jp8CuSoDywDCLhg\"\n        src=\"/static/727db4899b27ba045e53f860e3bfad31/fcda8/1__nA3n6X__jp8CuSoDywDCLhg.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/727db4899b27ba045e53f860e3bfad31/12f09/1__nA3n6X__jp8CuSoDywDCLhg.png 148w,\n/static/727db4899b27ba045e53f860e3bfad31/e4a3f/1__nA3n6X__jp8CuSoDywDCLhg.png 295w,\n/static/727db4899b27ba045e53f860e3bfad31/fcda8/1__nA3n6X__jp8CuSoDywDCLhg.png 590w,\n/static/727db4899b27ba045e53f860e3bfad31/37523/1__nA3n6X__jp8CuSoDywDCLhg.png 720w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4>References:</h4>\n<p>On Expo Snack you might have some issue, Please refer this link for some information: <a href=\"https://github.com/welldone-software/why-did-you-render/issues/58\">https://github.com/welldone-software/why-did-you-render/issues/58</a></p>\n<p>Link to github repo: <a href=\"https://github.com/welldone-software/why-did-you-render\">https://github.com/welldone-software/why-did-you-render</a></p>","frontmatter":{"titl